{"word":"G4556 - σάρδιος - sárdios - sar'-dee-os - Sardius","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σάρδιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sárdios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sar'-dee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sardius</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பதுமராகம் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sard, sardius, a precious stone"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Proper adjective from an uncertain base; <i>sardian</i> (<a href=\"#/G3037 - λίθος - líthos - lee'-thos/3037\">G3037</a> being implied), that is, (as noun) the gem so called: - sardius.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}